{"tid":1960100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2刀賊闖天水圍停車場　劫走職員2千元現金及手機","createTime":"2020-04-06T02:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T03:47:25.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"50c46065293f52a5764957420e76cb26991ceeb5","tid":1960100,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C02BhHz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC02BhHz.jpg&h=83c3ebab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日(6日)凌晨2時許，2名男子闖至天水圍天業路社區健康中心附近一露天停車場，用鐵棍擊毀更亭玻璃趟窗，繼而亮刀指嚇一名當值女職員，喝令她交出身上財物，女職員在利刀脅迫下不敢反抗，遭賊人掠去2,000元現金、一部約值4,500港元手機及一部約值1,000港元的遊戲機，得手後隨即跳上灰色七人車逃去無蹤，職員及後報案求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員封鎖現場調查，在附近兜截惜無發現，並翻看現場及一帶閉路電視錄影片段了解案發經過，追查賊人下落，案件交元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進。據悉，兩賊均年約30至40歲，案發時戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MPsQ6A6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMPsQ6A6.jpg&h=af35ea22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200406/mobile/bkn-20200406025027552-0406_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200406%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200406025027552-0406_00822_001.html&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=463fe893\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200406/mobile/bkn-20200406025027552-0406_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"59a9cbe4b8da60037630ae9c1eda42bbad7a4652","tid":1960100,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:23:34.000Z","msg":"留名等睇連仔偉論"},{"pid":"bd8d0772a0078a50ae9f0a8bc9b13299113200af","tid":1960100,"uid":810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:24:34.000Z","msg":"1,000港元的遊戲機係咩機呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b2f4f8f22c593d1408ab7e1fb7ddc870acaeaa","tid":1960100,"uid":15954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd8d0772a0078a50ae9f0a8bc9b13299113